A cyberpunk-style illustration of glowing neon socks with circuit patterns walking autonomously across a dark cityscape rooftop at night. The socks emit electric blue and magenta light trails as they move, leaving behind streams of binary data that dissolve into the rain-slicked surface. In the background, towering server buildings pulse with synchronized light patterns. The scene captures the concept of instant notification and real-time communication through the metaphor of socks literally "getting going" on their own. Rain droplets catch the neon reflections, creating a moody atmosphere of technology in motion.
